////////
Local Dependency
> Local to folder 
> Can be used only in one app 
> No Admin permisiion is require to install
> Added to package.json
# npm i packagename

global Dependency
> Install in laptop
> Can be use for any app
> Will not add to package.json
> Need Admin permisiion to install
> Only packages require befor app start 
# npm i -g packagename


dev Dependency
> Just like local
> Only Dependency used at the time of deployment

//////Step to install global dependencies//////
#window
> open cmd as administrator
> npm i -g packagename

#mac/linux
> open terminal
> sudo npm i -g packagename

///////CD////
npm i -g nodemon


