# Window
Inside C drive make folder by the name of data
C:\data
Inside data make folder by the name of db
C:\data\db


# mac & linux
> open terminal
> sudo mkdir data/db


//////
# params
> what we pass after / in url
> We need to define params in route
> Complusory to pass parameters if defined
# Query params
> what we pass after ? in url
> No Need to define params in route
> Not Complusory to pass QueryParams